{"tid":86715,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死2隻]山西罐車墮黃河支流洩毒物　傳300萬人停水","createTime":"2017-01-19T09:30:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-19T11:38:36.000Z","uid":32407,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a74c103fd26add0c54a85082a4c2ec5f80af358b","tid":86715,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T09:30:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170119/photo/bkncn-20170119143709324-0119_05011_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170119%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170119143709324-0119_05011_001_01b.jpg&h=c6f43d27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n裝載有毒粗苯的罐車墮河，毒物恐已流至黃河。（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n山西運城新絳縣三林鎮汾河橋，昨日上午9時許有一輛裝載約28.66噸有毒粗苯（煤熱解後產物）的罐車與一輛客車碰撞，導致罐車跌入黃河支流汾河，罐車上兩人死亡。其後罐車因破裂出現洩漏，恐粗苯已流入汾河。有消息稱，當局已緊急命令下游汾河及離黃河約200公里地區水廠停止採水，約300萬人要停止用水。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，粗苯是一級毒物，易燃、易爆，易中毒。據中國人權民運信息中心引述消息指，出事地點離黃河110公里，以汾河流速每小時5公里計，洩漏的粗苯估計今天中午已到達黃河。汾河下游的新絳、稷山、河津、萬榮4縣目前已搭建活性碳壩攔截吸附，防止污染物進一步擴散。而河南的三門峽水庫監測部門現正展開工作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75a6c1b30ab9b7aedff9186be3fde78d4b21b6e7","tid":86715,"uid":44455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T09:54:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b62e30bd7011abd271e5ab5d8e6dc3804573805","tid":86715,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T10:03:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"692d908a5323307ef51a2db22e3e85f1d1641a11","tid":86715,"uid":53261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T10:05:16.000Z","msg":"天滅"},{"pid":"33f343089f3bd7a1f75d4d9e014877cd05e08f54","tid":86715,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T10:10:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da06b6c3589c3411391e4142e64b713b83c74fe5","tid":86715,"uid":61636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T10:12:02.000Z","msg":"死十個當五傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19c63d9b795862c16abbe24248ac70bc3917cf91","tid":86715,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T11:38:36.000Z","msg":"人黎，同我餵廢老飲水"}]}